SELECT
	"BulkEmail"."Id",
	"BulkEmail"."CategoryId",
	"BulkEmail"."SendStartDate",
	"BulkEmail"."StatusId",
	"BulkEmail"."LaunchOptionId"
FROM
	"public"."BulkEmail"
	INNER JOIN "public"."SendingEmailProgress" ON ("SendingEmailProgress"."BulkEmailId" = "BulkEmail"."Id")
	LEFT OUTER JOIN "public"."Campaign" ON ("Campaign"."Id" = "BulkEmail"."CampaignId")
WHERE
	"BulkEmail"."StatusId" IN (@P1, @P2, @P3, @P4, @P5)
	AND "Campaign"."CampaignSchemaUId" IS NULL
	AND "SendingEmailProgress"."SendStartDate" < @P6
	AND "SendingEmailProgress"."SendStartDate" > @P7
